title: Sawyer Beckett's Baby Mama Drama Guide For Dummies
description: After going through pregnancy at her side, listening to all the mumbo-jumbo jargon strangers in white coats spewed at me, just to have my woman do the exact opposite the minute we left their office- I decided to help my fellow man.In a language we actually speak.If you've got a Baby Mama, pick up this short, simple guide and thank me later.
author: S.E. Hall
